 - Для экспериментального исследования выбрано 6 регионов республики. Разделение территории на 6 зон (южная, северная, средняя зона и Ферганская долина). Это город Ташкент, Ташкентская, Сырдарьинская, Самаркандская, Кашкадарьинская, Наманганский области и Республика Каракалпакстан. Весна в 6 районах нашей республики

bfunksiyaHaqida.en:
The main activities of the Scientific-Research Institute of Environmental and Nature Protection Technologies: 
 - reduction of air pollution in the emissions of harmful substances from industrial enterprises; 
 - prevention of underground and surface water pollution,
 - creation of modern, resource-saving, environmentally friendly technologies for cleaning natural, industrial, domestic waste water, cleaning sediments formed in the process of waste water treatment; 
 – work with production and consumption waste (toxic industry, agriculture, disposal and processing of household waste); 
 - development of regulatory and methodological documents in the field of environmental protection.
 - solving the problems of ecological safety, environmental protection and rational use of natural resources, rational use and conservation of land and water resources.
 The main tasks of the institute : 
 – conducting in-depth fundamental and applied research on the analysis of the current state of the environment, the impact of pollutants on flora and fauna; 
 - development of fundamentally new and effective methods and technologies for reducing air pollution, water and land resources, preserving biological diversity, waste processing and disposal; 
 - development, experimental design of technical means for domestic and production purposes, which ensure the reduction of pollution of atmospheric air, water and land resources, as well as waste processing and disposal; 
 - adaptation and implementation of advanced foreign technologies and innovations in the field of ecology and environmental protection; 
 - participation in the development of standards and requirements for environmental problems and environmental protection; development of cooperation with foreign scientific research institutions and centers in the field of protection, organization of scientific conferences, seminars, joint research, projects, internships and staff training; 
 - participation in the training of highly qualified personnel, retraining of teachers of higher educational institutions and experts in the field of ecology and environmental protection at the level of international standards. Activity on economic contracts
- PQ of the President of the Republic of Uzbekistan on April 21, 2017 - In connection with the implementation of the decree No. 2916 ”On the measures of fundamental improvement and development of the waste management system in 2017-2021”, the institute ”conducts experimental studies and timing works on determining the norms of solid household waste collection in the territory of the Republic of Uzbekistan”.
– ” Development of an energy-efficient method of comprehensive recycling of car tires to obtain commercial products. Development of a technology for comprehensive dry processing of used car tires. Development of a new technological scheme of the processing plant for the total and annually produced potential of rubber products and used polymer materials using environmentally friendly and economically acceptable methods and technology. (The work was carried out on initiative, there are rules for laboratory tests).
 - We have experience in the development of environmental projects. production of products from components), LLC ”MAX MILLING LEADER” (for the organization of DSU production), LLC ”MAXAM UZBEKISTAN” LLC (for the organization of production of cartridge emulsion explosives intended for the mining industry) LLC ”METAL SOLUTION TECHNOLOGIES” (for the establishment of a workshop for the production of sanitary-technical items (brass fittings), etc.
 - Development of technology for the purification of gas waste from gas processing plants from sulfur oxides by the sorption-catalytic method using ash and syrup waste from TES. Industry and heat the hard chi of energy use of the sorption-catalytic system used for the treatment of gas emissions from power plants, and then for the treatment of industrial waste water. 
 - 6 regions of the republic were selected for experimental research. Division of the territory into 6 zones (southern, northern, middle zone and Ferghana Valley). These are the city of Tashkent, Tashkent, Syrdarya, Samarkand, Kashkadarya, Namangan regions and the Republic of Karakalpakstan. Spring in 6 regions of our republic

